A platter of tacos for the Illumina RFP team! I don't have enough :taco:!
@Steve Bubb for working graphics magic  messy whiteboard pictures
@Natalie Sheffield for adding late-in-the-game finesse while under deadline pressure
@Ali Groepper @Raghav Jupally for your expertise and collaboration in building net-new content for a data & analytics bigger story
@rebecca.weber for diving in and helping wherever asked
Also to Prakash for driving to the finish line, to Viral for his client insights, and to Florin for being willing to dig in and elevate the story. :extreme-teamwork:

It's skeleton crew this week :skeleton_srgrafo:
But still seeing my team get praise from clients!
"Wow @Alex Krumins , this is AWESOME! I have been trying SO hard to figure this out!!!! THANK YOU!"
@Liz King taking something new on :slightly_smiling_face:
@Astha Saxena managing a lot of work she doesn't typically own like a champ!
:taco:

